type.description:
## Still

---


[Fluid Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/fluid_condition_types/still)

Checks whether this state describes a still (i.e. not flowing, i.e. source) fluid.

Type ID: `origins:still`

---

### Examples

```json
"fluid_condition": {
    "type": "origins:still"
}
```
